(start and a)Gamepad 1:
    b for intake motor
    left trigger for rotation down
    right trigger for rotation up
    dpad up for extending XRail
    dpad down for retracting XRail
    right stick x-axis to control horizontal movement of the box
    left stick y-axis to control vertical movement of the box
(start and b)Gamepad 2:
    left stick y-axis to control forward and backward movement of the robot
    right stick x-axis to control turning movement of the robot
    a for latching
    left_bumper for lowering latch mechanism
    right_bumper for raising latch mechanism
    x for stopping all processes
    y for resuming all processes

